      "rationale": "The 120-point holdout validation set covers 5 flow rates (2, 3, 4, 5, 6 L/min) and 4 rotational speeds (1500, 2000, 2500, 3000 RPM) plus boundary conditions, encompassing the COU operating envelope. All test conditions were drawn from the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump benchmark dataset."
