      "acceptanceCriteria": "Feedforward neural network architecture is appropriate for continuous regression of hemolysis index from shear stress field summary statistics.",
      "rationale": "A feedforward neural network with ReLU activations is well-suited to the smooth, continuous mapping from pump operating parameters and shear stress statistics to the hemolysis index. Literature supports use of deep regression networks for blood damage surrogate modeling (Biswas et al., 2023). Architecture selection was based on prior art and training loss convergence."
    },
