      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input features (flow rate, rotational speed, geometric tolerance parameters, shear stress summary statistics) are physically motivated and span the COU operating space.",
      "rationale": "Seven input features were selected: volumetric flow rate, impeller rotational speed, three geometric tolerance parameters (clearance gap, blade angle, outlet width), volume-averaged shear stress, and 95th-percentile shear stress. All features are physically motivated by the Giersiepen hemolysis power-law model and span the COU operating envelope."
