    "rationale": "The ML surrogate neural network model satisfies all 7 assessed credibility factors at or above required levels for MRL 2. Holdout validation demonstrates MAE = 0.031 RH units and R² = 0.974, meeting the acceptance criterion of MAE < 0.05 and R² > 0.95. Worst-case operating point identification is confirmed. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The credibility evidence package supports acceptance of the ML surrogate for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions in the CPB COU.",
